OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Fgenerally dry with clear periods and
OL,9,Fthe odd shower in the northwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,12,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,13,Fbubbling up by afternoon.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,16,Fand very warm with some sunshine on
OL,17,FMonday. Staying dry on Tuesday and
OL,18,FWednesday with some warm sunshine in
OL,19,Fthe east, but cloudier in the west at
OL,20,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
